"{\"uid\": \"patheos.com-blogs-faith4today-2024-07-olympic-opening-ceremony-offends-many-christians\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"This despicable parody of the Last Supper was part of the Olympic Opening Ceremonies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 85, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This despicable parody\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 22}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 26, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 50}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Opening Ceremonies\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 84}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Image courtesy of Must Read Alaska The Olympic Games in Paris opened last night with great excitement and fanfare, only to be subjected to this \\\"parody\\\" of the Last Supper with Jesus and the Apostles replaced by men in drag.\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997553436815, \"rank\": 2.44656163241424e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Image courtesy\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"Alaska\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"great excitement\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 187}, {\"ngram\": \"fanfare\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 199}, {\"ngram\": \"this \\\"parody\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"the Apostles\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"drag\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While I am not sure who in the Paris Olympic Committee thought this was a great idea, but it went over like a lead balloon on social media.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997553436815, \"rank\": 2.44656163241424e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great idea\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"a lead balloon\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us take a look.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"a look\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I guess it depends upon your perspective.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your perspective\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I find \\\"parodies\\\" like the one forced on us last night as extremely offensive and disrespectful.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"parodies\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I personally believe that there was a clear intent to insult our Lord and all followers of Jesus as well as Church teaching, but we really do not know and frankly I honestly do not care.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.o