nd\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.9988046610265168, \"rank\": 0.0011961496553078625, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"past history\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"the response\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fear can be an effective tool in controlling the narrative.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fear\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"an effective tool\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"the narrative\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While I think it is fair and we should be expected to voice our concerns and share our feelings about this disgusting event, as true followers of Jesus we will abide by His words in the Bible: Matthew 5: 11-12:Blessed are you when they insult you and persecute you and utter every kind of evil against you [falsely] because of me.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our concerns\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"our feelings\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"this disgusting event\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"true followers\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"His words\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bible\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"every kind\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rejoice and be glad, for your reward will be great in heaven.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your reward\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"heaven\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus they persecuted the prophets who were before you.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prophets\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luke 6: 35-36:But rather, love your enemies and do good to them, and lend expecting nothing back; then your reward will be great and you will be children of the Most High, for he himself is kind to the ungrateful and the wicked.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_6\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luke 6\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_6\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_6\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your enemies\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"good\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"your reward\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"the Most High\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Be merciful, just as [also] your Father is merciful.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your Father\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jesus was mocked and disrespected by many during His earthly ministry.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His earthly ministry\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jesus never reacted or responded to the taunts or the verbal and physical abuse.\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the taunts\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"the verbal and physical abuse\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Granted, scenes like we saw last night can be infuriating, but following Jesus is about peace, non-violence, and forgiveness.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scenes\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jesus asks us to trust Him to address those that wrong us because of our beliefs.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.975295897052876, \"rank\": 0.02532977801343385, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngr